{"tid":923499,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"兩中國桌球手打假波 于德陸遭重罰停賽十年","createTime":"2018-12-01T09:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T09:48:52.000Z","uid":152376,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6b7669de3e3acf1d4179b4cdbbfbf9bfcfa0dfc7","tid":923499,"uid":152376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T09:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181201/large/1543656879_0cc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181201%2Flarge%2F1543656879_0cc7.jpg&h=2c75ca18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n于德陸被重罰停賽十年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181201/large/1543656792_7279.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181201%2Flarge%2F1543656792_7279.jpg&h=1176191b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曹宇鵬被罰停賽六年<br />\n<br />\n世界桌球聯會周六宣佈，兩位中國桌球手曹宇鵬和于德陸因為在2016至2017年期間因為造假操控賽果，被重罰禁賽6年及10年。<br />\n<br />\n世界桌球聯會經過長達兩年的調查後，周六發表報告，証實28歲的曹宇鵬在2016年1月至12月期間，在當中的三場比賽中操控賽果並且從中得益，他認罪後已經在今年五月起被暫時禁賽，最終被判罰停賽6年，不過當中有三年半刑期獲得緩刑。<br />\n<br />\n而31歲的于德陸亦被控於2016年2月至2017年11月期間在五場賽事中造假，並且獲得利益，被世界桌球聯會重罰停賽10年零9個月。<br />\n<br />\n兩人的調查報告發表後，中國桌球協會亦隨即發表聲明，強烈譴責兩人「不聽勸阻、一意孤行，對桌球這項運動和個人都造成了難以挽回的損失」，額外向兩人作出處罰，判處曹宇鵬禁止參加中國國內賽事兩年，而于德陸就被重罰禁止參與國內賽事10年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20181201/58980774\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181201%2F58980774&d=6QdQly7TZhMNNtULIaCvDpUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=62a30a02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181201%2F58980774&h=5f4c553b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20181201/58980774</a>"},{"pid":"ad0b583ff40f7ae5cb941f07cb67b677ece5c5d9","tid":923499,"uid":221490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:01:25.000Z","msg":"中國桌球協會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074096a5cf4883e3c3f2570404b9f8a0d84a7a4a","tid":923499,"uid":34352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:02:51.000Z","msg":"抵死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4cbce01590f882f58829569f67b4dbce59af33","tid":923499,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c221c0d6110ed1fdf77c9d9101007868d692b7","tid":923499,"uid":37586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad0b583ff40f7ae5cb941f07cb67b677ece5c5d9","tid":923499,"uid":221490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:01:25.000Z","msg":"中國桌球協會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:06:56.000Z","msg":"報告一出後即變棄卒,THIS IS CHINA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d9778d5c458ef98e674e83273bea08e9e693b4","tid":923499,"uid":91631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:10:56.000Z","msg":"不聽勸阻、一意孤行<br />\n<br />\n即係一早知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8efc3b9dfc7dd5ad5da0376f46dd00aa3eb671bb","tid":923499,"uid":41524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:48:30.000Z","msg":"睇個樣都知係仆街"},{"pid":"2cb41ed3a2a9afbe1478977e4b780f49174a3dc2","tid":923499,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T10:49:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">判處曹宇鵬禁止參加中國國內賽事兩年，而于德陸就被重罰禁止參與國內賽事10年。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國國內同國內有乜分別？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d906a57e58bd7b77dd7dc8c8e2cc41a0523878d","tid":923499,"u